  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dance of Blades: Master the Rhythm of Carnage</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With just <strong>Light Attack | Heavy Attack | Dash</strong>, unleash over 40 combat combos—carve your path through the chaos. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/7091033b79a5bd143fca08233c1cd37d.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/7091033b79a5bd143fca08233c1cd37d.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/7091033b79a5bd143fca08233c1cd37d.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Skill Mechanic</strong>: Press <strong>Attack</strong> right <strong>before</strong> dashing ends to chain evasion into lethal counterattacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1820dd7057fbb477b8edd9d6d4dae026.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1820dd7057fbb477b8edd9d6d4dae026.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1820dd7057fbb477b8edd9d6d4dae026.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat</strong>: Crush foes with Heavy Attack lunges or shred hordes with rapid Light Attack flurries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/420a4284c319c63919013be087d2ed82.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/420a4284c319c63919013be087d2ed82.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/420a4284c319c63919013be087d2ed82.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deflect Projectiles</strong>: Parry arrows and spells back to enemies with perfectly timed Heavy Attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/0f759238b89726e8acc90fd0b19b9a7c.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/0f759238b89726e8acc90fd0b19b9a7c.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/0f759238b89726e8acc90fd0b19b9a7c.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Precision Counters</strong>: Strike during enemy wind-up phases to deal 3x Weakpoint Damage. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/f121a4f5d79d7182e30329867e1367ee.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/f121a4f5d79d7182e30329867e1367ee.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/f121a4f5d79d7182e30329867e1367ee.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Brutal Creativity</strong>: Ambush bosses via environmental shortcuts or exploit their attack patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1026e5a27b987cf4fe5793a18a9a2e17.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1026e5a27b987cf4fe5793a18a9a2e17.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/1026e5a27b987cf4fe5793a18a9a2e17.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize throwable axes and explosive barrels to control the battlefield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/5b8262190a1ebb8e8def8bbb264bb83b.poster.avif?t=1769350117\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/5b8262190a1ebb8e8def8bbb264bb83b.webm?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340210/extras/5b8262190a1ebb8e8def8bbb264bb83b.mp4?t=1769350117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Purity of Skill</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No gear grind—victory depends solely on your mastery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 difficulty tiers cater to both newcomers and masochists.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enemy Ecosystem</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horde Onslaught</strong>: Carve \"blood corridors\" through undead swarms in decaying towns and frozen catacombs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stealth & Carnage</strong>: Backstab grunts, cripple elites with ambushes—choose your slaughter style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nightmare Mode</strong>: Increased enemy aggression and rare loot drops for true blade virtuosos. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration & Controls</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guided Open-World</strong>: Linear critical path with environmental clues hinting at secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control Freedom</strong>：Full rebinding for controllers, mice, or retro WASD+JKL keyboard setup. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ Not for players seeking gear builds/base-building/cinematic narratives. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer's Note</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"This is an action forge tempered over three years—  <br>Every frame of blade arc tested 100+ times, every boss an exam of pure mechanics.  <br>No mercy. Only steel speaks here.\"</p>",
