ists.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enemy Ecosystem</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horde Onslaught</strong>: Carve \"blood corridors\" through undead swarms in decaying towns and frozen catacombs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stealth & Carnage</strong>: Backstab grunts, cripple elites with ambushes—choose your slaughter style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nightmare Mode</strong>: Increased enemy aggression and rare loot drops for true blade virtuosos. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration & Controls</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guided Open-World</strong>: Linear critical path with environmental clues hinting at secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control Freedom</strong>：Full rebinding for controllers, mice, or retro WASD+JKL keyboard setup. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❌ Not for players seeking gear builds/base-building/cinematic narratives. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer's Note</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"This is an action forge tempered over three years—  <br>Every frame of blade arc tested 100+ times, every boss an exam of pure mechanics.  <br>No mercy. Only steel speaks here.\"</p>",
